Class AttributeConstants

java.lang.Object
se.swedenconnect.opensaml.sweid.saml2.attribute.AttributeConstants
public class AttributeConstants extends Object
Contains constants for all attributes defined in section 3.1 of "Attribute Specification for the Swedish eID Framework".
